description: Welcome to this beautifully maintained 2-bedroom, 2-bath condo, built in 2017 and freshly painted for a move-in ready experience. Ideally situated just moments from the Red Line, with effortless access to the Seaport, Downtown Boston, and major commuter routes, this home offers the perfect blend of style, comfort, and convenience.Entire condo is bright and offers an open living space featuring hardwood floors, high ceilings, and direct access to a private deck—perfect for morning coffee or evening relaxation. The modern kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, and ample cabinetry, seamlessly flowing into the dining and living areas. Both bedrooms are generously sized, with the primary suite offering a walk-in closet and a sleek, en-suite bath. Additional features include central air, in-unit laundry, extra storage, and garage parking for one car. This professionally managed elevator building offers peace of mind and low-maintenance living.
